main event: An unidentified flying object was observed hovering over Teheran, Iran on 16 July.
interesting points: The object appeared to be giving off multicolored lights., Russian air base personnel witnessed the aerial object., The object interfered with the operation of jet engines on various planes., An unidentified flying object was later tracked on radar., Additional sightings included an object flying from north to south over Rasht, Iran on 26 July 1957.
sighted object: a strange hovering object emitting multicolored lights
